START program

Create main application window

Display search input box
Display search button
Display random cocktail button

WHEN user clicks Search button
    Get text from search input
    Send request to Cocktail API using search text
    IF cocktail data is found
        Display cocktail name
        Display ingredients list
        Display recipe
        Display cocktail image
    ELSE
        Display "Cocktail not found" message
    END IF
END WHEN

WHEN user clicks Random Cocktail button
    Send request to Cocktail API for random cocktail
    IF data is returned
        Display cocktail name
        Display ingredients and measurements
        Display recipe
        Display cocktail image
    ELSE
        Display error message
    END IF
END WHEN

END program


